message.content: cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MED, cs.NEURON - This paper deals with medical image analysis using deep neural networks, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) categories. The paper also discusses weakly supervised learning, which is a subfield of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper focuses on medical imaging (cs.MED) and the use of neural networks (cs.NEURON) for segmentation tasks.
